desc_long								关于这款游戏							BECOME THE MASTER (mini) THIEF!Can you escape with the loot? Play as the Master Thief and steal as much as you can. Burgle houses in order to obtain some sweet, sweet loot.  But be careful not to get caught!. Your objective is simple, search the area for items which are exchangeable for money. Each level you pass will increase in difficulty. The more difficult the level is the more loot you will obtain. Avoid the owner at all costs! If he catches you, well, you lose everything! including your money!						
